law.history: Repealed 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 230, sec. 41, effective July 15, 2002. -- Amended 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 300, sec. 11, effective July 14, 2000. -- Created 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 414, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1998.
